snippet.title: [FEE3 2020] Immortal Sword by BwdYeti
snippet.description:
This video was submitted by BwdYeti, showcasing his project Fire Emblem: Immortal Sword (FE7x). 

FE7x is, remarkably, the only project to maintain a "perfect attendance award" for FEE3, having appeared in every one of our annual showcases.

In light of recent community events, for this year's FEE3, we're doing a fundraising drive for RAINN, the Rape, Abuse, and Incest National Network! Anything you can spare helps! All proceeds go directly to the charity itself, through RAINN's own website.

RAINN general information: https://www.rainn.org/about-rainn
Proceeds can be donated here: https://fundraise.rainn.org/give/t319650/#!/donation/checkout

Learn more about this project at: http://www.bwdyeti.com/fe7x
FEE3 main discussion: https://feuniverse.us/t/fee3-2020-10-2-10-18-20/8656/1
